<p>英 /'peɪmənt/    美 /'peɪmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 付款：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>mobile payment
移动支付</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Payment</strong> may <strong>be made</strong> in cash, by cheque, or by credit card. 
可用现金、支票或信用卡付款。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 支付的款项：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>receive a payment
收款</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make <strong>monthly payments</strong> on a car 
每月分期付款买车</p></div></div>